# Copy to .env and fill in. .env is git-ignored and copied read-only into
# worktrees (with GitHub tokens stripped — the Coordinator on the main checkout
# is the only agent that pushes or opens PRs).

# GitHub identity for THIS Crescendo project. gh + git (via the repo-local
# credential helper set by conductor-setup) authenticate as this token's account,
# isolated from any other `gh auth login` you use in parallel. Use a fine-grained
# PAT with Contents/Issues/Pull requests: Read and write on this repo.
GH_TOKEN=

# (Optional) other shared credentials your agents need — DB URLs, API keys, etc.
# These ARE copied into worktrees (read-only). GitHub tokens above are NOT.
